---
const { } = Astro.props;
---

<section>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="py-12 md:py-20">
      <div class="py-4 sm:py-6 lg:py-8">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap md:-mx-8">
          <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 px-0 sm:px-8">
            <div class="mb-12 lg:mb-0 pb-12 lg:pb-0 border-b lg:border-b-0">
              <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold font-heading">
                What is our goal? To provide businesses with viable, well tested and ground-breaking blockchain solutions resulting in exciting new features, products or services, better user experiences, improved security or greater market reach.
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                We pride ourselves on aligning our goals align with our clients’, allowing us to achieve the most effective solutions that have real impact on company growth. In business, tech is a means to an end ¬– profitability. We get that. We create solutions that anticipate your needs both today and tomorrow.
              </p>
              <div class="w-full">

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 px-0 sm:px-8">
            <ul class="space-y-12">
              <li class="flex md:-mx-4">
                <div class="pr-4 sm:pl-4">
                  <span
                    class="flex w-16 h-16 mx-auto items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold font-heading rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600">
                    1
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4">
                  <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">
                   Data
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    The blockchain is capable of making revolutionary changes for businesses in the same way that the internet revolutionized communication. The main open source platform behind this transformation is Hyperledger, which is maintained by the Linux Foundation.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex md:-mx-4">
                <div class="pr-4 sm:pl-4">
                  <span
                    class="flex w-16 h-16 mx-auto items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold font-heading rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600">
                    2
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4">
                  <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">Cloud</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    We have helped businesses move their office to the cloud for almost 9 years now. You can save tens of thousands on physical hardware by giving your employees cloud based workstations. Cut out the need for ongoing IT support.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex md:-mx-4">
                <div class="pr-4 sm:pl-4">
                  <span
                    class="flex w-16 h-16 mx-auto items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold font-heading rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600">
                    3
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4">
                  <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">Support</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    We will work closely with your management team to identify cases for blockchain use in existing processes, such as B2B payments, smart contracts, full supply chain tracking, data security, transaction facilitation, or back office platforms for human resources.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>